text.tspan: DARKVISION: Dim -> bright w/i 60' & dark -> dim
HEART: Commoners try to help me & will fight
w/me if I'm alone, unless I'm a danger to them
THIEVES' CANT: 4x longer but can hide messages
CAT'S BURST: 1 turn w/2x speed, move 0' to regain
ASSASSINATE: Adv on attack vs target that hasn't
had a turn yet. Hit on Surprised ---> Critical
SNEAK ATTACK: if hit w/finesse or range weapon
AND (have Adv w/attack OR target w/i 5' of
